				<a href="{{path('app_products')}}" class="btn btn-outline text-capitalize">Our products</a>
			</div>
		</section>
		{# -----------DIVISOR #}
		<div class="divisor divisor-lg"></div>

		{# -----------------BAR #}
		<section class="mt-5">
			<h2 class="headers text-capitalize text-center">Our Bar</h2>
			<p>The bar, with its polished wood and softly glowing lights, exudes a cozy sophistication that invites intimate conversations over perfectly crafted cocktails. As you move through to the terrace, a tranquil oasis awaits, adorned with lush greenery and twinkling fairy lights that cast a gentle glow over the tables.
			</p>
			<p>Here, friends clink glasses, couples share stolen glances, and families unwind together amidst the harmonious blend of laughter and the subtle hum of contentment. Whether savoring a signature drink or indulging in a delightful meal, Tasty Drink effortlessly weaves an atmosphere where every moment is infused with joy and connection, making it a cherished destination for all who seek camaraderie and unforgettable experiences at Tasty Drink Bar & Shop.</p>

